(metadata:
"NPC", "OldInrah",
"title", "Asking Koh-Inrah for Odd Jobs",
"topic", "\"Is there anything that needs doing around the Pilgrim's Rest?\"",
"topicDetail", "If you're in need of a little pocket change, or just to get on her good side.",
"cooldown", 1,
